00:56:14.150 --> 00:56:15.320 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:56:15.320 --> 00:56:22.630 align:middle line:84%
So for the AD
regular set, before I

00:56:22.630 --> 00:56:24.450 align:middle line:84%
