01:06:38.160 --> 01:06:44.350 align:middle line:84%
At first it looks like an unholy
mess, but it's the same as this.

01:06:44.350 --> 01:06:48.480 align:middle line:90%


01:06:48.480 --> 01:06:52.200 align:middle line:84%
And so it's delta to
the minus T over 2,

01:06:52.200 --> 01:06:54.900 align:middle line:84%
which is B, which is
what we were hoping for.

01:06:54.900 --> 01:06:59.520 align:middle line:90%


01:06:59.520 --> 01:07:03.080 align:middle line:90%
This is a smiley face.

01:07:03.080 --> 01:07:06.920 align:middle line:84%
But let me mention
another scenario.

01:07:06.920 --> 01:07:08.440 align:middle line:90%
Scenario 2.

01:07:08.440 --> 01:07:13.080 align:middle line:84%
Maybe T1 is bigger
