01:07:31.320 --> 01:07:35.200 align:middle line:90%
I'm in the C domain.

01:07:35.200 --> 01:07:38.520 align:middle line:90%
I get rho to the 1 minus T1.

01:07:38.520 --> 01:07:42.520 align:middle line:84%
And when I evaluate this,
