01:07:42.520 --> 01:07:45.490 align:middle line:90%
I'm in the A domain, which is 1.

01:07:45.490 --> 01:07:49.150 align:middle line:90%


01:07:49.150 --> 01:07:51.670 align:middle line:84%
And that's not what
